import com.eviware.soapui.support.XmlHolder
def holder = new XmlHolder(messageExchange.responseContentAsXml) log.info holder def sessionId = messageExchange.responseHeaders["Session-Id"] log.info sessionId.get(0)
assert(sessionId.get(0) != null)
holder.namespaces['ns']='https://primus.grindr.com/2.0/session'; def xmppToken = holder.getNodeValue('//ns:Response/ns:xmppToken') log.info xmppToken assert(xmppToken != null) messageExchange.modelItem.testStep.testCase.setPropertyValue("xmppToken",xmppToken) messageExchange.modelItem.testStep.testCase.setPropertyValue("sessionId",sessionId.get(0))
def httpStatus = messageExchange.responseHeaders["Status"] log.info httpStatus assert(httpStatus.get(0) == "200 OK")
def httpStatus = messageExchange.responseHeaders["Status"] log.info httpStatus assert(httpStatus.get(0) == "200 OK")
